featured_reviews.review_id:
Masha Allah Nice Masjid
------------------------------------------
Allah Ta'ala Ne Tamaam Insaanon Ki Duniya Ki Zindagi Aur Aakhirat Yaani Marne Ke Baad Ki Zindagi Ki Kaamyabi Sirf "DEEN" Mein Rakhi Hai, Allah Ta'ala ke Hukum Ko Pura Karne Aur Aap  Ki Bataaye Huwe Tareeqon Ke Mutaabiq Chalne Ka Naam "DEEN" Hai. Lihaaza Har Musalmaan Ke Liye Zaroori Hai Ke Woh Apni Zindagi Ke Har Shobe Mein Allah Ta'ala Ka Hukum Aur Hazrat Muhammad  Ka Tareeqon Maaloom Kar Ke Us Par Amal Kare Aur Us Ko Logon Tak Pohnchaane Ki Fikr Kare.
Is Liye Bahot Zaroori Hai Ke Musalmaan Apni Dunyawi Mashguliyan Ke Saath Kuchh Waqt Nikaal Kar Kam Az Kam Itna Ilm Haasil Kare Jo Us Par Farz Hai Aur Koshish Kare Ke Ziyaada Se Ziyaada Ilm Haasil Kare Aur Us Par Amal Kare.
---*---*--*--*---*---
Allah Ta'ala se Dua hai ke Jo Log Masjid Ku Banaye aur Aabaad  Karte Hai Allah Une Aabaad Kare aur une ki Maghfirat kare..
(Ameen)
(Suma Ameen )
-----------------------
+----#--*--#----+
 Allah ke Zikir Karo 
+----#--*--#----+

Masha Allah Nice Masjid

Allah Ta'ala has no respect for the world, the life and the hereafter means death, only "DEEN" is kept in me; "Deen" Lihaaza Har Musalmaan Ke Liye Zaroori Hai Ke Woh Apni Zindagi Ke Har Shobe Mein Allah Ta'ala Ka Hukum Aur Hazrat Muhammad  Ka Tareeqon Maaloom Kar Ke Us Par Amal Kare Aur Us Ko Logon Tak Pohnchaane Ki Fikr Kare.
Is Liye Bahot Zaroori Hai Ke Musalmaan Apni Dunyawi Mashguliyan Ke Saath Kuchh Waqt Nikaal Kar Kam Az Kam Itna Ilm Haasil Kare Jo Us Par Farz Hai Aur Koshish Kare Ke Ziyaada Se Ziyaada Ilm Haasil Kare Aur Us Par Amal Kare.

I pray to Allah Ta'ala that those who build and decorate the Masjid, may Allah decorate one and forgive others.
(Ameen)

featured_reviews.review_id:
Surrounded by forest, located about 4 kms from devanahalli new bus stand, serves the purpose of being an Eidgah very well since it should be located far from the population and still reachable, its a peaceful place and thus perfect for offering Eid salah (namaz, prayers). It was a wonderful and peaceful experience for me today to go there by walking in the morning and offering two rakah Eid-ul Zuha namaz and listen to the post prayer khutbah (a brief Spiritual Speech), there were some stalls of ice cream also which the kids loved, they enjoyed kulfi and ice creams after the khutbah and the environment was very peaceful and enjoyable at the same time, the weather was cool with slow wind which makes the leaves sing and fall...
For me it was an amazing experience may Allah accept our salah, sacrifices, duwas, grant us Jannah and make us among those who are the successful in true sense, Aameen.
